    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, so it's kind of a gray area depending on how it's linked. what if it's just some random technical glitch/malfunction in the grid that isn't tied to war or anything? like just total chaos and nothing makes sense why it happened. how would a lawyer argue that's an unforeseeable disruption rather than just bad luck or poor maintenance?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
